data.description: Welcome to a fantastic opportunity for both investors and those seeking a convenient living space. This condominium is strategically located, offering proximity to Quail Springs Mall, the newly established Scissortail Elementary School, and easy access to Kilpatrick Turnpike. The property is also extremely close to all major amenities, making it walkable to dining, shopping, entertainment, and more. Easy access to public transportation makes this condo even more attractive both as a rental or primary living space. This condominium is a perfect blend of modern living and investment potential. Whether you are looking for a comfortable home or a strategic investment, it checks all the boxes. Don't miss out on this opportunity! Schedule a viewing today.
